<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV39">
<l>veṟpeṭuttu vēlainīrka lakkiṉāya taṉṟiyum</l>
<l>veṟpeṭuttu vēlainīrva rampukaṭṭi vēlaicūḻ</l>
<l>veṟpeṭutta viñcicūḻi laṅkaikaṭṭa ḻittanī</l>
<l>veṟpeṭuttu mārikātta mēkavaṇṇa ṉallaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You picked up a hill and churned the ocean water;</l>
<l>Other than that, You lifted up the hill and dammed up the ocean water,</l>
<l>You destroyed Laṅkā surrounded by the ocean and encircled by ramparts made</l>
<l>Of hills. Aren’t You the cloud-hued [Lord] who lifted up the hill and protected</l>
<l rend="indent">from the rains?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
